Fuck college, fuck a "real" job! Music is your life! You're a hometown hero! You're in at least two local bands and are thinking of forming a third. You sleep on your friend's couch, eat your friend's food, and borrow your friend's car. You frequent the dark city bars and hang with the other rockers and groupies. You wear dirty jeans, well-worn t-shirts, and your hair is a mess. You're sinister and mysterious and look as if you don't give a shit. You worship the Rolling Stones, MC5, and your older brother's band. You're gonna make it big one of these days, you can just feel it.

I deleted the goddamn comments.  Matt hasn't gotten them yet, and never will.  He never did shit, so stop being a cocksucker.  ...get a fucking life.  You are SO PATHETIC.  You're NEVER going to see my fucking boyfriend again.  I'm NEVER speaking to you again.  You two are NEVER going to fight, so you'll NEVER have the chance to gang up on him w/like ten other ppl so he doesn't have a chance.  Go get laid... maybe you won't have so much fucking aggression all the time.  And you KNOW you started this shit so dont turn it around.  I don't ask for money from people.  Ask my goddamn friends if u don't believe me.  If anything, I GIVE things to people.  I don't know HOW many times I've given out money to my friends when they really needed it.  And why the fuck should you care anyways?  You have MY shit!  Stay out of my life.  I DON'T WANT you in it.  Seriously.  GET IT IN YOUR HEAD.  Seeing you makes me want to fucking vomit all over myself.  Stop trying to start shit with people who don't deserve it because you think it makes you a badass.  Well, you're still NOT a badass, and you fucking know it.  This is the last time I'm speaking (typing... I'll NEVER SPEAK) to you ever again.  And drop off my goddamn guitar.  I know you've had time.

Bye.
